==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Expectorant
<hw>Ex*pec"to*rant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>expectorans</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>expectorare</ets> to drive from
the breast: cf. F. <ets>expectorant</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>Tending to facilitate expectoration or to promote discharges of
mucus, etc., from the lungs or throat.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos>
<def>An expectorant medicine.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Expectorate</ent>⟦br⟧
